<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="190r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l23"><expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>Swarcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> Plawen dem <expan>Elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l24">geſchehen iſt / daʒ Jr euch von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden darumb <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l25"><expan>gnedigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> darẏnne beweiſet vnd darcʒu getan habt / des wir etc vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l26">daʒ Jr auch furbaſʒ ewr gnad hilff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darcʒu vvenden wöllet / das etc </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter"><ab facs="#facs_381_r1l27"> <expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Pünaw 
<del rend="strikethrough">R<gap reason="illegible"/></del> Rats / Graf <expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Swarcʒburg von Ramſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_381_r1l28"><expan>Heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Geraw vnd <expan>Eberhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von holbach <expan>Rıtt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſimilit<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan> <expan>muta<ex>n</ex>d<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_381" id="190r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>Swarczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> Plawen dem <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Geschehen ist, daz ir euch von <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gnaden darumb
                                <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>gnedigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> darynne beweiset und darczu getan
                        habt, des wir etc. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir auch furbasz
                        ewr gnad hilff und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darczu wenden wöllet,
                        das etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Pünaw, rats; graf
                                <expan>Gunth<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Swarczburg von Ramsz;
                                <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Geraw und
                                <expan>Eberhart<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Holbach,
                                <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>similit<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>d<ex>is</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
